TextEng: What was this Drawl creature?
You're dressed like a city guard. Why were you captured?
Text: 도시 경비대 복장이네. 왜 붙잡힌 거지?

TextEng: You look like city guard. Why you trapped here?
Text: 너 도시 경비처럼 보여. 왜 여기 갇혔어?

TextEng: Who this Drawl creature guy?
I have questions about Drawl.
Me gots questions about Drawl.
Text: 나 드롤에 대해 물어볼 거 있어.

TextEng: I have questions about you, Walters.
Text: 월터스, 너에 대해 물을 게 있어.

TextEng: Me gots questions about you, Walters.
Text: 나 너한테 물어볼 거 있어, 월터스.

TextEng: I have questions about the "others" you mentioned.
Text: 네가 말한 '다른 녀석들'에 대해 물을 게 있어.

TextEng: Me gots questions about "others" you mention.
Text: 나 네가 말한 '다른 애들' 물어볼 거 있어.

TextEng: I should get moving. What will you do now?
Text: 난 움직여야겠어. 넌 이제 어떻게 할 거지?

TextEng: Me should get moving. What you do now?
Text: 나 가야 돼. 너 이제 뭐 해?

TextEng: I assume he wasn't always like this?
He not always like this, was he?
If he's just some kid, who gave him this power?
Text: 그가 그냥 꼬마라면, 이 힘은 누가 준 거지?

TextEng: If he just some jerk, who give him power?
Text: 그 그냥 꼬맹이면, 힘 누가 줬어?

TextEng: I need to ask something else.
Me ask something else.
Why did you quit the gang and become a guard?
Why you quit gang to become guard?
Text: 너 왜 갱단 그만두고 경비대 됐어?

TextEng: Where are you supposed to be stationed?
Where you supposed to patrol?
What happened to them?
What happen to those guys?
Back to my general questions...
Back to general stuff questions...
I think you should make a break for it.
You maybe make a break for it, okay?
Just wait here until I clear things out.
You waits for me to bash streets safe.
Text: 나 길 안전하게 만들 때까지 여기서 기다려.

TextEng: You should just run to the gate.
Yous just run there, okay?
No gang cause all this stuff around here.
Text: 갱단이 이런 일 다 일으킨 거 아니야.

TextEng: What is going on around here?
What going on around heres?
A gang couldn't have caused all this trouble.
Text: 갱단이 이 모든 문제를 일으킬 리 없어.

TextEng: Who helped this Drawl?
Who behind Drawl for this?
Why would someone corrupt a gang like that?
Text: 대체 누가, 왜 갱단을 그렇게 타락시킨 거지?

TextEng: Why someone make gang bad like that?
Text: 왜 누가 갱단 그렇게 망치게 해?

TextEng: Should killing Drawl have stopped the zombies?
Text: 드롤을 죽였으면 좀비들이 멈췄어야 하는 거 아닌가?

TextEng: Should making Drawl dead stop zombies?
